  h3 Procedures
  p.
    In this study, you will play an online social game with simulated players. In every round,
    you will be given a hypothetical awkward scenario at work and your task will be to choose
    your own reaction from a pool of cards to the situation. In addition, you will be asked to
    complete a brief demographic questionnaire.
  p.
    In total, the study should take no longer than 30 minutes to complete.
  h3 Participant Requirements
  p.
    Participation in this study is limited to individuals age 18 and older who currently reside in the
    United States, have at least basic computer proficiency, and have the ability to read and
    understand English.
  h3 Risks
  p.
    The risks and discomfort associated with participation in this study are no greater than those
    ordinarily encountered in daily life or during other online activities. The survey may cause
    boredom or fatigue.
  p.
